      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a stunning, swirl-free deep metallic paint, the exterior is flawless, having been exclusively garage-kept and protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero wear or creasing, the original floor mats are pristine, and that unmistakable 'new car' scent is still present. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist sensors, functions perfectly and without lag. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed solely at authorized dealerships and meticulously documented in a thick binder of receipts included with the sale. With incredibly low mileage and a whisper-quiet, powerful ride, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly immaculate, investment-quality condition.",
